# Environment Configuration for Mail Hooks

## Node Environment
NODE_ENV=production
LOG_LEVEL=info

## Database (Neon PostgreSQL)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@db.neon.tech/mailhooks?sslmode=require

## SMTP Engine Configuration
SMTP_PORT=25
ATTACHMENT_STORAGE=memory
MAX_FILE_SIZE=5242880

## Web UI Configuration
UI_PORT=3000
API_KEY=your-secret-api-key-here

## Optional: Email Forwarding Configuration
WEBHOOK_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/webhooks/incoming
WEBHOOK_TIMEOUT=10000
